It&#39;s a fold-down antenna I got from Ron Ricketts, the creator of the
Mini, via April Slaughter, who arranged for me to get the first
commercially available box.  It&#39;s not part of the package that comes
with the Mini.  A wire antenna works too.  I don&#39;t always use it --
depends on the reception.

Rosemary
